{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "568f22cb-5b2b-46de-bfb8-edf92af5818d",
    "name": "Magic Class Session 2 10 Arcamulet",
    "sceneId": "981d126b-abc7-430a-abb4-e912340c59e6",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "3daf4516-7bbd-4f32-89f1-5fa794c55bca",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "46c5c239-c9ad-46e6-90d8-692d4e89ed34",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "7bd335dc-25eb-47a8-8ca8-175248b13c02",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Today, we shall be using all that Mojo you stored in the Spongea runestone together with some additional Mojo in order to create a Magical protection device known as an Arcanulet.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "eb159e3c-506a-45c0-a543-0822c41f2159",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "This item helps to shield you from the ill-effects of magical spells and reduces the damage that you take from magic. You should wear this Arcanulet whenever you go into places of high magic.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "5312e8d2-2b18-46d1-a53c-9e200fa3bdba",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "We shall be using the knowledge of Spellcasting, Enchanting, and Alchemy to create this Arcanulet. It is the culmination of everything you've learned over this course.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "1d269176-9d74-41aa-a6f2-f4c5db154fab",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Are there any questions before we concentrate upon our magic?",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "id": "3b5487b1-2fbd-44af-bf77-fdf3dc8c2407",
                    "type": "nodes.improveSkill",
                    "skill": "Magic",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "65728ac9-91f2-46a5-9c66-b3604a06191e",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "55839d71-fdec-4773-86dd-518f88388aad",
                            "text": "Ask About the Class Ending",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "a3332467-6bed-48de-8fbd-5dbd942b5d67",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Does this mean that we are almost finished with this class? It feels like we just got started. There's so much to learn about Magic!",
                                    "emotion": "4",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "2e09aeae-4847-4cee-bd8d-62033a2eaacd",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Unfortunately, <i>Tempus Fugit</i> and so, this class draws near to the closing. For the penultimate class tomorrow, we will have a brief exam on your knowledge and then we shall finish up on the following day.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "2",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "ed06c4fc-f8f2-4f39-99d7-53e3cf1c048a",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "It has been an interesting and pleasurable experience teaching magic to you mundanes. ",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "40cf3953-5ab5-493d-b65e-ccebe7feb9ae",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "74",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "34ed59aa-77ff-488d-9db1-1017b7b00155",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "5c0ad07c-128e-4ea9-930e-8821107c5922",
                            "text": "Ask About the Arcanulet",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "e48a8e5f-cd05-4f55-b815-2cc35a53cdc8",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "What does the Arcanulet actually do? Does it work like the Null runestone to block magic?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f73f90d7-66f4-4985-a686-69f1c2510b36",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Excellent question, but no, the Arcanulet is not a form of wearable Null spell. Unlike the Null runestone, it does not negate magic, so you can safely wear other magical items or cast your own spells.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "27266a50-5c9a-43f4-ae42-48e51ddc9a2c",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "The Arcanulet absorbs and dissipates magical spells targeted upon the wearer of the amulet. Some of the Mojo it absorbs is used to create the spell shield. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "2b0273d2-1e8e-40fb-9d9f-48e39f4c02b2",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "While the Arcanulet cannot block all hostile magic from harming you, it will prevent Life Drains from Ghosts or reduce damage from the Frost Sprays of Revenants.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "f5437f34-a3a4-4fce-822a-37e724f08125",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "74",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "67506efc-1f7e-4925-9668-f4ba1941b0bf",
                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "796f29f8-685e-4756-8fff-2c2c500ab048",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "7",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "b8c8e26b-021e-425d-86a7-2aa4022dd4bb",
                            "text": "Say Something Snarky About Wizards",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "fc5f7342-03d7-41bc-a09d-dc23ce28e42e",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "So, if Wizards are so smart, why don't they solve the world's problems by destroying all the monsters?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "709fd5dc-55e8-4245-92c3-0fcf62e7af02",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Wizards are smart enough to know that the worst monsters in the world don't look like monsters. Tyrants can be more murderous and devastating than the greediest of Dragons.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "19eb2000-0897-4b1d-a3fc-e10a6b031ba8",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "If you destroy a tyrant with the wave of your staff, another will just take his place. The most powerful of spells cannot undo the power of an Evil man. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d4d7b090-b66e-48a5-9ace-ae13bb389318",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Wizards with all their intelligence cannot fix the way the world is. It takes great compassion, wisdom, and determination to change the world for the better. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "8eea29ca-0e4b-424c-a30a-2fc790ed7829",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "That's why the world needs Heroes like you.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "95599c01-0111-4b58-91d2-bcf17ada0b10",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "74",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "8413b652-0eb1-472e-be43-a03f3de05182",
                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
